{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2061","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"讓龜山更乾淨！宗豪向環保局提出5大建議","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2061-1.png","sequence":2061,"category1":"B. 營造永續環境","category2":"B.1 提升環境保護作業","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1AiGYHW4dr/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-05-02T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"讓龜山更乾淨宗豪向環保局提出-5-大建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓龜山更乾淨！宗豪向環保局提出 5 大建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今天我在議會針對環保局提出 5 項建議，希望市府能加快腳步、確實改善，為龜山打造更乾淨的生活環境："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1️⃣ 一趟收運不轉運"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n環保局調整日夜間收運量能，配套措施要跟上！建議市府編列預算補助社區購買垃圾子車，落實「一趟收運、不中途轉運」的目標。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2️⃣ 龜山人口持續成長，清潔人力要補上！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n不只戶籍人口增加，移動人口也多，清潔隊負擔越來越重，應增補人力，減輕第一線壓力！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n3️⃣ AI 幫忙盯亂丟垃圾！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n長庚商圈、龜山市區商圈、重劃區工地等熱點應優先導入 AI 偵測系統，維護市容整潔！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n4️⃣ 工地揚塵有效管理，守護居民健康！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n建議未來捷運棕線施工區導入 AI 揚塵灑水系統，全天候監控並自動灑水，降低空污、守護周邊居民。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n5️⃣ 偷排汙染不能放過！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n針對科學園區、工業區等地方，加強稽查，防止偷排廢氣與汙水。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我會持續監督！讓我們的生活環境更乾淨、更宜居！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2061-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2061-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"讓龜山更乾淨宗豪向環保局提出-5-大建議","depth":2,"text":"讓龜山更乾淨！宗豪向環保局提出 5 大建議"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2061.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2061.md","_extension":"md"}